== oVirt Node Release Notes ==

== 2.2.1 Release Notes ==

* UEFI installation does not work with internal drives, only usb drives [https://bugzilla.redhat.com/show_bug.cgi?id=761540 Bug 761540]
* Registration directly from ovirt-node will fail [https://bugzilla.redhat.com/show_bug.cgi?id=782663 Bug 782663]
* Adding oVirt Node through the engine interface will fail [https://bugzilla.redhat.com/show_bug.cgi?id=782660 Bug 782660]
** There is a workaround available in this [http://gerrit.ovirt.org/#change,1117 patch]
** Needs to be applied on the ovirt-engine server to vds_installer.py in /usr/share/ovirt-engine/scripts/
* Some hardware seems to fail to boot the Node correctly
** Fails to load the TUI when booting the first time
** Seen on IBM x3650 Servers
** Cannot reproduce on desktop hardware or virtual machines
* See Current Backlog for other issues [[Node_Backlog]]

